responses.content:

Given statement: If the glip was slogged (P), then the glip was not tragged (not Q).

Contrapositive: If the glip was tragged (Q), then the glip was not slogged (not P).

The contrapositive is logically equivalent to the original statement. Therefore, we can infer the contrapositive from the given statement.
